bibliographical review, documental analysis of the municipal urban legislation
of Varginha, Elói Mendes, Três Corações and Três Pontas, besides the
legislation applied to the spaces studied, and cartographic, comparing to the
urban evolution of the aerial images of Google Earth , in order to analyze the
influence of urban equipments on the territorial and socio-environmental
configuration of Varginha, observing the advance of urbanization and the
emergence of a new centrality imposed by the industrial and logistic districts.
